to dedicate the rest of his life to Sino-Japanese friendship, and
is ready to come to serve the farmers in China at any time they
need him.
</P>
<P>
He said the Chinese side has given him a lot of support over
the past 16 years, and this made it possible for the technique of
planting rice with fewer seedlings to spread widely in China.
