-- Israeli Labor Party leader Ehud Barak is under investigation
for his relations with Gregory Lerner, who is suspected of
affiliation to active Russian Mafia in Israel.
</P>
<P>
The Egyptian Gazette:
</P>
<P>
-- Jordan and Kuwait resumed direct air flights Wednesday for
the first time since Iraq's 1990 invasions of Kuwait in the latest
move towards normalizing ties. 
