<HEADLINE> Mugabe Urges Zimbabwean Companies Lead in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, July 10 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwean President Robert Mugabe
on Wednesday urged Zimbabwean companies to take the lead in
investment in their own country instead of relying solely on
foreign investment for a meaningful transformation of the
economy.
</P>
