<HEADLINE> Boat Disaster Claims 20 Lives in Eritrea </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, July 9 (Xinhua) -- Twenty people were killed and
18 were reportedly missing when a boat carrying 65 persons
illegally from Eritrea to a neighboring area capsized in the Red
Sea, the Voice of Eritrea reported today.
